    "title": [
      "[Wyvern Plaza]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "Broad, shallow stairs of alternating flint and slate lead down toward the river and up toward the top of the bluff.  Terraced gardens line the sides of the stairways, their flowers and dwarf fruit trees exquisitely espaliered and cultivated.  Between the two sets of stairs, a large plaza paved in checkerboard squares of flint and slate surrounds a sculptural fountain.  Four curved benches, placed at the points of the compass, provide an opportunity to sit and watch elven society meander by."
    ],
